U(firstName+"/lBl34",{content:"First Name"})
lastName=I(part2,{type:"ref",ref:"iNpC3"})
U(lastName+"/lBl34",{content:"Last Name"})
U("Dca2fsz",{layout:"vertical",gap:20,padding:32})
```

The response is:

